      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cverse2",
        "text": "And it came to pass, when he reigned, that he {k} smote all the house of Jeroboam; he left not to Jeroboam any that breathed, until he had destroyed him, according unto the saying of the LORD, which he spake by his servant Ahijah the Shilonite:",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "And it came to pass, when he reigned, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "i",
            "class": "",
            "text": "that",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
